WEBVTT

00:10.600 --> 00:11.531
<i> PREVIOUSLY ON "GREENLEAF"...</i>

00:11.533 --> 00:13.132
THEY HAD TO REMOVE
YOUR OVARIES.

00:13.134 --> 00:14.398
I CAN'T HAVE CHILDREN?

00:14.400 --> 00:15.731
YOU KNOW THE RULES --

00:15.733 --> 00:17.399
NO CONTACTING THAT BOY.

00:17.401 --> 00:18.932
OR HAVE I NOT BEEN CLEAR?

00:18.934 --> 00:20.531
WHAT DO YOU KNOW
ABOUT CRYPTOCURRENCIES?

00:20.533 --> 00:21.565
NOTHING.

00:21.567 --> 00:23.131
PEOPLE ARE GETTING RICH.
CAN WE?

00:23.133 --> 00:24.465
YOU CAN HAVE THE HOUSE.

00:24.467 --> 00:25.865
I'LL TAKE CARE
OF THE IRS BILL.

00:25.867 --> 00:27.265
BUT YOU HAVE
TO LEAVE THE CHURCH.

00:27.267 --> 00:29.199
Mae: I AM SORRY
THAT YOU WERE SCARED.

00:29.201 --> 00:30.165
BUT YOU KNOW WHAT?

00:30.167 --> 00:32.499
DON'T BEAT ME UP.
IT WON'T FIX IT.

00:32.501 --> 00:33.532
FIX<i> YOU.</i>

00:33.534 --> 00:35.165
WE'RE DIVORCING.
[ CONGREGATION GASPS ]

00:35.167 --> 00:36.398
WE WILL ALWAYS BE FAMILY.

00:36.400 --> 00:37.699
AND I'M STILL YOUR BISHOP.

00:37.701 --> 00:40.232
I WILL CONTINUE ON
AS YOUR FIRST LADY

00:40.234 --> 00:42.332
UP THROUGH
"A DAY WITH LADY MAE."

00:42.334 --> 00:46.065
WHERE WE WILL HAVE
A VERY, VERY SPECIAL GUEST,

00:46.067 --> 00:50.065
MY DEAR, DEAR FRIEND
MAXINE PATTERSON.

00:50.067 --> 00:52.065
IS THAT LEGAL DEFENSE FUND
OF YOURS OPERATIONAL YET?

00:52.067 --> 00:53.399
WHY?
Woman in Collierville

00:53.401 --> 00:55.132
just killed her husband
while he was sleeping.

00:55.134 --> 00:56.899
SHE'S SAYING
IT WAS SELF-DEFENSE.

00:56.901 --> 00:58.965
Grace: SO, SHE KILLED HIM
WITH A HAMMER,

00:58.967 --> 01:01.165
WHICH SOUNDS UNATTRACTIVE
IF YOU'RE SOMEONE WHO'S THINKING

01:01.167 --> 01:03.098
ABOUT BACKING HER,
BUT APPARENTLY,

01:03.100 --> 01:05.399
IT'S SOMETHING HE'D USED
ON HER A FEW TIMES BEFORE.

01:05.401 --> 01:07.732
IF YOU SAY
THAT THIS IS THE CASE,

01:07.734 --> 01:09.665
THEN THIS IS THE CASE.

01:09.667 --> 01:17.265
♪♪

01:17.267 --> 01:24.732
♪♪

01:24.734 --> 01:26.998
[ KEYBOARD CLACKING ]

01:27.000 --> 01:33.065
♪♪

01:33.067 --> 01:39.199
♪♪

01:39.201 --> 01:41.665
[ CLEARS THROAT ]

01:41.667 --> 01:43.365
[ KEYBOARD CLACKING ]

01:43.367 --> 01:50.565
♪♪

01:50.567 --> 01:51.732
[ SCREAMING ]

01:51.734 --> 01:53.199
NO!

01:53.201 --> 01:59.232
♪♪

01:59.234 --> 02:00.632
[ GRUNTS ]

02:00.634 --> 02:02.298
Sophia: MOM?

02:02.300 --> 02:03.732
♪♪

02:03.734 --> 02:05.832
MOM.
WHAT ARE YOU DOING?

02:08.900 --> 02:10.232
NOTHING.

02:10.234 --> 02:12.332
WAS THAT ABOUT THE LADY
WHO KILLED HER HUSBAND?

02:12.334 --> 02:13.899
THE ONE ON THE NEWS?

02:13.901 --> 02:15.165
[ BREATHES DEEPLY ]

02:15.167 --> 02:18.131
YEAH, I'M GOING TO MEET
WITH HER TOMORROW,

02:18.133 --> 02:21.265
SEE IF ABOUT -- I DON'T KNOW --
IF I CAN HELP HER.

02:21.267 --> 02:22.198
UH...

02:22.200 --> 02:23.732
WE CAN TALK LATER.

02:23.734 --> 02:24.665
NO, NO, NO.

02:24.667 --> 02:27.998
I'M GONNA GO TO BED SOON,
SO...

02:28.000 --> 02:29.265
WHAT DO YOU NEED, BABE?

02:29.267 --> 02:31.265
[ BREATHES DEEPLY ]

02:31.267 --> 02:33.499
CAN YOU TALK
TO PASTOR RONA?

02:33.501 --> 02:34.765
ABOUT WHAT?

02:34.767 --> 02:35.998
LITTLE SAINTS.

02:36.000 --> 02:38.831
MM. SHE'S NOT TAKING NO
FOR AN ANSWER, HUH?

02:38.833 --> 02:41.532
NOPE,
BUT I DON'T WANT TO DO IT.

02:46.200 --> 02:49.431
I KNOW YOU GOING THROUGH
A LOT RIGHT NOW, BABY.

02:49.433 --> 02:50.699
I KNOW IT. I DO.

02:50.701 --> 02:52.165
I'M NEVER GONNA BE
ABLE TO TALK TO THEM

02:52.167 --> 02:53.431
THE WAY I USED TO.

02:53.433 --> 02:55.365
I DON'T EVEN KNOW IF I
BELIEVE IN GOD ANYMORE.

02:57.967 --> 03:00.098
HAS YOUR GRANDMOM
HEARD YOU SAY THAT?

03:00.100 --> 03:01.798
'CAUSE SHE'S GONNA HAVE
YOU UP AT 6:00 A.M. WITH ZORA

03:01.800 --> 03:03.232
IF YOU'RE NOT CAREFUL.

03:03.234 --> 03:04.698
[ CHUCKLES ]

03:04.700 --> 03:06.865
WILL YOU TALK TO HER OR NOT?

03:06.867 --> 03:08.332
[ SIGHS ]

03:08.334 --> 03:10.865
YEAH, I'LL TALK TO HER.

03:10.867 --> 03:12.965
[ SIGHS ]
THANK YOU.

03:18.734 --> 03:25.765
♪♪

03:25.767 --> 03:32.865
♪♪

03:32.867 --> 03:35.332
♪ AMEN ♪

03:37.934 --> 03:39.198
♪ ALL RIGHT ♪

03:39.200 --> 03:40.398
♪ AMEN ♪

03:40.400 --> 03:43.332
♪ UH-HUH, HMM ♪

03:43.334 --> 03:45.899
♪ OOH-OOH, OOH ♪

03:48.934 --> 03:50.365
♪ WELL ♪

03:53.867 --> 03:56.798
♪ OH-OHH, OHH ♪

03:56.800 --> 04:02.332
♪ OOH, OOH, OOH, OOH ♪

04:02.334 --> 04:05.299
♪ AMEN, AMEN ♪
♪ OH ♪

04:08.800 --> 04:10.665
♪ YEAH ♪

