23:10.033 --> 23:11.865
[ DOOR OPENS,
FOOTSTEPS APPROACHING ]

23:14.167 --> 23:16.898
IF YOU COULD
JUST SIGN THESE.

23:16.900 --> 23:19.532
I'D BE HAPPY TO.

23:19.534 --> 23:21.265
HOW YOU DOING, KARINE?

23:21.267 --> 23:22.465
HOW'S YOUR DAY GOING?

23:22.467 --> 23:24.132
JUST BUSY
SHOWING THE ROPES

23:24.134 --> 23:27.132
TO MAXINE PATTERSON'S
MS. SOMETHING.

23:27.134 --> 23:29.932
I'M SORRY,
BUT THAT GIRL IS SLOW.

23:29.934 --> 23:31.732
I SEE.
[ CHUCKLES ]

23:31.734 --> 23:34.932
I JUST KEEP
PRAYING FOR PATIENCE.

23:34.934 --> 23:38.598
"STEEL SECURITY."

23:38.600 --> 23:40.932
WHAT'S THAT FOR?

23:40.934 --> 23:46.065
UH, SECURITY
FOR "DAY WITH LADY MAE."

23:46.067 --> 23:48.232
SECURITY?

23:54.934 --> 23:57.799
SO, "DAY WITH LADY MAE" IS
GONNA BE AT CALVARY THIS YEAR.

23:57.801 --> 24:00.465
THAT BIG, HUH?

24:00.467 --> 24:03.865
IT MAY VERY WELL BE, YES.

24:03.867 --> 24:07.598
AND WHEN WERE YOU GOING
TO TELL ME ABOUT IT?

24:07.600 --> 24:11.332
WELL, I JUST ONLY GOT THE
DEPOSIT BACK FROM THE TEMPLETON,

24:11.334 --> 24:13.198
AND I DIDN'T WANT TO SAY
ANYTHING UNTIL I FOUND --

24:13.200 --> 24:14.865
OH, YOU DIDN'T WANT TO SAY
ANYTHING PERIOD, MAE.

24:14.867 --> 24:16.298
JUST ADMIT IT.

24:16.300 --> 24:17.898
WELL, SINCE YOU'RE HERE,

24:17.900 --> 24:19.732
YOU SHOULD KNOW THAT,
WITH MAXINE,

24:19.734 --> 24:21.598
THERE WILL BE
EXTRA COSTS THIS YEAR.

24:21.600 --> 24:23.598
WELL, THEN LET MAXINE
PAY FOR IT.

24:23.600 --> 24:26.198
WHY NOT HAVE HER RENT THE
FedExForum WHILE SHE'S AT IT?

24:26.200 --> 24:28.999
I MEAN, IF YOU'RE EXPECTING
SUCH A FLOOD OF PEOPLE.

24:29.001 --> 24:33.332
JAMES, HAVING MAXINE'S PRESENCE
IS A BOON FOR THE CHURCH.

24:33.334 --> 24:35.132
OH, PFFT.
BETTER TO HAVE HER HERE,

24:35.134 --> 24:38.198
WHERE IT REALLY COUNTS.

24:38.200 --> 24:39.998
AND WHAT ABOUT
MY SILVER JUBILEE?

24:40.000 --> 24:41.398
OH, YOU MEAN
THE SILVER JUBILEE

24:41.400 --> 24:43.398
THAT I WAS JUST INFORMED ABOUT
THIS MORNING?

24:43.400 --> 24:44.598
WHAT ABOUT IT?

24:44.600 --> 24:47.265
JUST DON'T YOU
FORGET OUR DEAL.

24:47.267 --> 24:48.965
AND WHAT DEAL IS THAT,
DEAR?

24:48.967 --> 24:52.098
AFTER THIS "DAY WITH
LADY MAE," YOU'RE GONE.

24:52.100 --> 24:53.598
[ KNOCK ON DOOR, DOOR OPENS ]

24:53.600 --> 24:57.065
Gloria: SORRY.
LADY MAE.

24:57.067 --> 24:58.799
THE COMMITTEE IS GATHERED
IN THE CONFERENCE ROOM.

24:58.801 --> 25:00.465
THANK YOU, GLORIA.

25:02.467 --> 25:05.065
[ DOOR CLOSES ]

25:05.067 --> 25:07.932
AND AS FOR ME AND
MY FUTURE PLANS,

25:07.934 --> 25:11.998
I WILL GO WHERE
THE LORD LEADS ME TO GO,

25:12.000 --> 25:14.265
AND I ASSUME
YOU'LL DO THE SAME.

25:14.267 --> 25:22.532
♪♪

25:22.534 --> 25:30.798
♪♪

25:30.800 --> 25:32.265
ALL RIGHT.

25:32.267 --> 25:34.065
THERE YOU GO.

25:42.400 --> 25:44.432
[ CLEARS THROAT ]

25:46.133 --> 25:47.332
WHAT?

25:47.334 --> 25:48.532
DON'T "WHAT" ME.

25:48.534 --> 25:51.265
YOU KNOW I KNOW WHEN
SOMETHING'S GOING ON WITH YOU.

25:51.267 --> 25:53.798
SO, YOU WANT
TO TALK ABOUT IT?

25:53.800 --> 25:55.498
PROBABLY SHOULDN'T.

25:55.500 --> 25:57.365
YOU KNOW I'M MARRIED

25:57.367 --> 26:00.598
TO THE ONE AND ONLY
BASIE SKANKS, RIGHT?

26:00.600 --> 26:05.065
I KNOW HOW TO KEEP A SECRET,
JACOB, SO TALK TO ME.

26:08.767 --> 26:10.498
COME ON.

26:10.500 --> 26:12.932
TALK TO ME, JACOB.
TELL ME WHAT'S GOING ON.

26:17.933 --> 26:20.998
YOU EVER...

26:21.000 --> 26:24.065
HAVE SOMEBODY THAT YOU KNOW
TREAT YOU LIKE THE PERSON

26:24.067 --> 26:26.398
THAT YOU USED TO BE
BACK IN THE DAY,

26:26.400 --> 26:27.998
BUT YOU'RE NOT
THAT PERSON ANYMORE?

26:28.000 --> 26:29.598
ARE YOU KIDDING ME?

26:29.600 --> 26:31.398
YOU KNOW
WHAT I'M TALKING ABOUT?

26:31.400 --> 26:33.598
YEAH, I KNOW WHAT
YOU'RE TALKING ABOUT.

26:33.600 --> 26:36.798
JACOB, DO YOU THINK
I'VE ALWAYS BEEN

26:36.800 --> 26:40.932
THIS HOLY CHURCH LADY
YOU SEE IN FRONT OF YOU?

26:40.934 --> 26:42.732
LIKE I DIDN'T GO OUT

26:42.734 --> 26:45.765
EVERY SATURDAY NIGHT,
TRYING TO GET MY SWERVE ON.

26:45.767 --> 26:48.565
WALKING INTO CHURCH ON
SUNDAY, EYES BARELY OPEN,

26:48.567 --> 26:52.432
PRAYING OTHER PEOPLE WAS
THINKING I WAS REALLY PRAYING.

26:52.434 --> 26:54.465
[ BOTH LAUGH ]

26:54.467 --> 26:58.732
AND, YOU KNOW, THOSE PEOPLE
WOULD LOVE TO BRING ME DOWN

26:58.734 --> 27:01.265
AND REMIND ME
OF THAT EVERY DAY,

27:01.267 --> 27:04.465
BUT I KNOW I'VE
BEEN FORGIVEN, SO...

27:04.467 --> 27:07.332
YEAH, SEE,
THAT'S JUST THE THING.

27:07.334 --> 27:10.598
I KNOW KERISSA FORGIVES ME,
BUT SHE'LL NEVER FORGET.

27:10.600 --> 27:14.165
AND THEN SHE WON'T
LET ME FORGET EITHER.

27:14.167 --> 27:16.099
AND I'M SICK OF IT.

27:18.967 --> 27:20.698
HMM.

27:20.700 --> 27:22.898
BRING IT IN.

27:22.900 --> 27:25.665
COME ON, BRING IT IN.
OH, GOD.

27:25.667 --> 27:27.532
IT'LL BE OKAY.

27:30.467 --> 27:32.598
IT'LL BE ALL RIGHT.

27:32.600 --> 27:40.432
♪♪

27:40.434 --> 27:48.465
♪♪

27:48.467 --> 27:56.565
♪♪

