BISHOP?

28:31.067 --> 28:32.798
HEY.
[ DOOR CLOSES ]

28:32.800 --> 28:34.398
JUST THE WOMAN
I WANT TO SEE.

28:34.400 --> 28:36.798
[ CHUCKLES ] I CAN'T SAY
I MIND MEETING IN PERSON,

28:36.800 --> 28:38.932
BUT IT DOES
HAVE ME CURIOUS.

28:38.934 --> 28:41.332
WHAT'S MY BISHOP UP TO NOW?

28:44.700 --> 28:46.365
OH.

28:46.367 --> 28:47.999
YOU FOUND MORE CASH.

28:48.001 --> 28:50.398
I FOUND MORE CASH.

28:50.400 --> 28:53.132
CASH I WOULDN'T GIVE
TO ANYONE ELSE.

28:53.134 --> 28:55.865
BUT I TRUST YOU...

28:55.867 --> 28:57.498
AND YOUR EXPERTISE.

28:57.500 --> 29:02.898
♪♪

29:02.900 --> 29:04.365
THANK YOU.

29:04.367 --> 29:06.732
♪♪

29:06.734 --> 29:08.465
[ GLASSES CLINK ]

29:08.467 --> 29:10.398
♪♪

29:10.400 --> 29:12.998
DO YOU BELIEVE HER STORY?

29:13.000 --> 29:14.532
WHAT, THAT HER HUSBAND
ABUSED HER?

29:14.534 --> 29:15.731
YEAH.

29:15.733 --> 29:17.765
OH, YEAH.
THAT PART RINGS TRUE.

29:17.767 --> 29:19.565
AND THERE'S A STRING
OF EMERGENCY-ROOM BILLS

29:19.567 --> 29:21.231
AND 911 CALLS, YES.

29:21.233 --> 29:23.565
SO, WHAT'S THE PROBLEM?

29:23.567 --> 29:25.865
THIS D.A.

29:25.867 --> 29:28.632
HE'S GONNA USE MY STORY
AGAINST HER...

29:28.634 --> 29:29.765
AGAINST ME.

29:29.767 --> 29:32.332
HE SAID AS MUCH
RIGHT TO MY FACE.

29:32.334 --> 29:33.865
SO WHAT?

29:33.867 --> 29:36.298
THAT WAS SELF-DEFENSE, TOO.

29:36.300 --> 29:39.265
I MEAN, I KNOW
IT WAS HELLISH, BUT...

29:39.267 --> 29:41.532
IT WAS SELF-DEFENSE, TOO,
RIGHT?

29:41.534 --> 29:44.165
-CALL SOMEBODY.
-I'M NOT CALLING ANYBODY...

29:44.167 --> 29:47.031
TILL YOU TELL ME
WHERE MY DAUGHTER IS.

29:47.033 --> 29:50.499
[ CHOKING ]

29:52.901 --> 29:54.031
RIGHT?

29:54.033 --> 29:56.565
[ BIRDS CAWING IN DISTANCE ]

29:56.567 --> 29:59.898
♪♪

29:59.900 --> 30:01.465
RIGHT.

30:01.467 --> 30:02.699
♪♪

30:05.700 --> 30:13.932
♪♪

30:13.934 --> 30:22.465
♪♪

30:22.467 --> 30:30.798
♪♪

30:30.800 --> 30:39.731
♪♪

30:39.733 --> 30:40.732
[ HORN HONKING ]

30:42.467 --> 30:44.665
[ HORN HONKING ]

30:44.667 --> 30:47.332
ALL RIGHT, ALL RIGHT! I'M
GOIN', I'M GOIN'. I'M GOIN'.

30:47.334 --> 30:53.198
♪♪

30:53.200 --> 30:58.865
♪♪

30:59.967 --> 31:01.632
YOU WANT TO PUT THAT DOWN?

31:01.634 --> 31:02.898
[ LAUGHS ]
HMM?

31:02.900 --> 31:05.898
NO. I'VE HAD ENOUGH
ALCOHOL FOR THE MINUTE,

31:05.900 --> 31:07.665
SO I'LL STICK
WITH MY WATER.

31:07.667 --> 31:10.798
WELL,
IF THAT'S YOUR PLEASURE.

31:10.800 --> 31:13.431
WHAT A DAY, THOUGH.

31:13.433 --> 31:15.165
YEAH.

31:17.367 --> 31:20.432
YOU KNOW,
I THOUGHT I'D COME HERE

31:20.434 --> 31:22.565
AND SING A FEW SONGS
AND THEN SKIP ON OUT.

31:22.567 --> 31:24.998
YEAH. [ CHUCKLES ]

31:25.000 --> 31:27.998
I FEEL RUN OVER.
DRAINED.

31:28.000 --> 31:30.332
BEING IN THE MIDST
OF ALL THAT GRIEF.

31:30.334 --> 31:32.198
YEAH.

31:32.200 --> 31:35.732
WELL, YOU KNOW,
PEOPLE COME HERE

31:35.734 --> 31:38.665
REELING FROM THE WORST THING
THAT'S HAPPENED TO THEM,

31:38.667 --> 31:41.665
AND YOU SOAK IT IN.

31:43.534 --> 31:46.198
WOW.

31:46.200 --> 31:47.332
I DON'T KNOW
HOW YOU DO IT.

31:50.834 --> 31:52.765
I DRINK.

31:57.734 --> 31:59.665
LADY MAE,
THANK GOODNESS WE CAUGHT YOU

31:59.667 --> 32:01.398
BEFORE YOU LEFT
FOR THE DAY.

32:01.400 --> 32:05.265
THE CATERER NEEDS A DEPOSIT
TODAY, OR THEY WON'T COMMIT.

32:05.267 --> 32:07.998
WHAT, AT SIX WEEKS OUT,
THEY NEED OUR MONEY?

32:08.000 --> 32:09.798
THEY'RE THE ONLY ONES
BIG ENOUGH TO HANDLE THE JOB,

32:09.800 --> 32:10.932
AND THEY'RE POPULAR.

32:10.934 --> 32:12.798
AND BISHOP'S
ALREADY LEFT FOR THE DAY.

32:12.800 --> 32:14.898
OH, NO PROBLEM.

32:14.900 --> 32:19.132
I WILL JUST TRANSFER MY MONEY
FROM MY PERSONAL ACCOUNT

32:19.134 --> 32:22.665
AND THEN HAVE THE CHURCH
WRITE ME A CHECK TOMORROW.

32:22.667 --> 32:24.598
THANK YOU SO MUCH.

32:24.600 --> 32:29.099
ONE MOMENT,
AND LET ME LOG IN.

32:29.101 --> 32:31.565
[ KEYBOARD CLACKING ]

32:33.934 --> 32:36.065
WAIT.

32:36.067 --> 32:37.832
UH...

32:40.733 --> 32:42.232
IS SOMETHING WRONG?

32:45.467 --> 32:48.798
UH...

32:48.800 --> 32:52.398
I DON'T KNOW, BUT...

32:52.400 --> 32:55.065
THERE IS DEFINITELY
SOMETHING AMISS.

32:55.067 --> 32:57.065
THEY NEED THE CHECK
BY THE CLOSE OF BUSINESS.

32:57.067 --> 32:58.365
GLORIA.

32:58.367 --> 32:59.499
YES?

32:59.501 --> 33:01.632
WOULD THE TWO OF YOU
EXCUSE ME?

33:01.634 --> 33:08.332
♪♪

33:08.334 --> 33:14.865
♪♪

33:14.867 --> 33:16.332
[ KEYBOARD CLACKS ]

33:16.334 --> 33:23.631
♪♪

33:23.633 --> 33:30.932
♪♪

33:33.633 --> 33:35.165
TALK TO MY MOTHER?

33:35.167 --> 33:37.065
NOPE. I WAS JUST TRYING
TO FIGURE OUT WHAT IT WAS

33:37.067 --> 33:38.398
I WANTED TO SAY
WHEN YOU WALKED IN.

33:38.400 --> 33:41.332
WHY?

33:41.334 --> 33:43.932
WELL...

33:43.934 --> 33:46.465
I THOUGHT WE SHOULD BOTH
GO OVER THERE TOMORROW

33:46.467 --> 33:48.865
AND BRING ZORA HOME.

33:51.467 --> 33:52.865
WHAT MADE
YOU CHANGE YOUR MIND?

33:55.534 --> 33:57.232
PRAYED ABOUT IT.

34:00.334 --> 34:01.665
THANK YOU.

34:03.000 --> 34:05.032
SORRY I GOT SO DUG IN.

34:06.734 --> 34:08.965
IT'S OKAY.

34:08.967 --> 34:13.632
I AM SORRY THAT
I BROUGHT UP ALL THAT STUFF

34:13.634 --> 34:16.365
ABOUT YOU
NOT FLYING RIGHT.

34:16.367 --> 34:18.032
THAT WASN'T FAIR.

34:20.267 --> 34:23.598
IT'S OKAY.
WE ALL MAKE MISTAKES.

34:23.600 --> 34:26.198
YES, WE DO.
[ CHUCKLES ]

34:26.200 --> 34:29.332
IT'S TRUE.

34:29.334 --> 34:32.665
[ BREATHES DEEPLY ]

34:32.667 --> 34:40.465
♪♪

34:40.467 --> 34:48.132
♪♪

34:48.134 --> 34:55.765
♪♪

35:01.600 --> 35:04.799
YOU EMPTIED
OUR SHARED ACCOUNT?

35:08.200 --> 35:11.398
IT'LL BE FULL
IN TWO WEEKS' TIME.

35:11.400 --> 35:12.865
MORE THAN FULL
IF ALL GOES WELL.

35:12.867 --> 35:14.198
SAYS MS. CROSS.

35:14.200 --> 35:16.598
SAYS CNBC
AND EVERYONE ELSE.

35:16.600 --> 35:19.132
INSIDER TRADING
IS NOT ILLEGAL YET,

35:19.134 --> 35:21.532
SO THE WORD ON THE STREET
IS THAT WE'LL BE --

35:21.534 --> 35:24.632
I WANT YOU
OUT OF THIS HOUSE TONIGHT.

35:29.134 --> 35:30.932
I'VE ALREADY MADE
ARRANGEMENTS TO STAY

35:30.934 --> 35:33.398
WITH PERCY
FOR THE SHORT TERM.

35:33.400 --> 35:34.598
I'LL BE LEAVING
IN THE MORNING.

35:34.600 --> 35:36.365
YOU'LL LEAVE TONIGHT.

35:40.000 --> 35:42.598
AND, THIS TIME,
TAKE IT ALL, JAMES.

35:42.600 --> 35:47.165
EVERY LAST TIE
AND PURPLE ROBE

35:47.167 --> 35:49.798
AND GAUDY KNICKKNACK.

35:49.800 --> 35:51.065
I WANT YOU OUT OF HERE.

35:51.067 --> 35:52.999
I WANT YOU GONE.

35:55.467 --> 35:57.065
AS YOU WISH, DEAR.

35:57.067 --> 36:03.098
♪♪

36:03.100 --> 36:08.998
♪♪

36:09.000 --> 36:10.299
[ KNOCK ON DOOR ]
[ CRYING ]

36:10.301 --> 36:11.365
Grace: YOU OKAY, BABY?

36:11.367 --> 36:13.632
[ SOBBING ]

36:14.634 --> 36:16.565
SWEETIE, WHAT ARE YOU DOING?
WHAT ARE YOU DOING?

36:16.567 --> 36:18.165
LEAVE ME ALONE!
NO, STOP IT, STOP IT.

36:18.167 --> 36:20.265
GIVE ME THAT.
STOP THAT!

36:20.267 --> 36:21.332
STOP IT!

36:21.334 --> 36:23.532
WHAT IS WRONG WITH YOU, HONEY?
WHAT'S GOIN' ON?

36:23.534 --> 36:27.432
THE BIBLE IS ALL LIES!

36:27.434 --> 36:30.332
YOUR GRANDDAD
GAVE YOU THIS BIBLE.

36:30.334 --> 36:32.265
[ SOBBING ]

36:35.734 --> 36:37.599
SWEETHEART.

36:39.000 --> 36:42.198
YOU FEEL WHAT YOU WANT
TO FEEL, YOU BE UPSET,

36:42.200 --> 36:43.532
BUT THIS IS NOT A LIE.

36:43.534 --> 36:45.865
HE LOVES YOU.
HE GAVE THIS TO YOU.

36:45.867 --> 36:48.398
DON'T THROW THAT AWAY.

36:48.400 --> 36:50.465
YOU WILL REGRET IT.

36:50.467 --> 36:53.465
♪♪

36:53.467 --> 36:57.198
I HATE THAT I CAN'T GO BACK.

36:57.200 --> 36:59.332
TO WHAT, HONEY?

36:59.334 --> 37:01.798
GO BACK TO WHAT?

37:01.800 --> 37:05.265
TO BEFORE I GOT SAVED.

37:05.267 --> 37:07.265
I JUST WANT
TO NOT KNOW GOD'S REAL

37:07.267 --> 37:09.398
SO I CAN JUST LIVE MY LIFE.

37:09.400 --> 37:11.332
COME HERE.

37:11.334 --> 37:14.798
I CAN'T FORGET HOW I FELT
THE DAY IN THE CHURCH

37:14.800 --> 37:17.598
WHEN I WENT
DOWN IN THE WATER.

37:17.600 --> 37:20.932
I DON'T WANT TO LOVE SOMEONE
WHO TREATS ME THIS BADLY.

37:20.934 --> 37:23.998
I JUST WANT TO LET GOD GO.

37:24.000 --> 37:29.065
I JUST WANT HIM TO LET ME
FORGET AND LEAVE ME ALONE.

37:29.067 --> 37:33.332
WHY WON'T
HE JUST LET ME GO?

37:33.334 --> 37:37.132
HE'S NOT GONNA LET YOU GO.

37:37.134 --> 37:39.332
AND I'M NOT
GONNA LET YOU GO.

37:39.334 --> 37:44.932
♪♪

37:44.934 --> 37:50.598
♪♪

37:50.600 --> 37:53.132
[ BREATHES DEEPLY ]

37:53.134 --> 37:58.665
♪♪

37:58.667 --> 38:04.132
♪♪

38:04.134 --> 38:09.599
♪♪

38:12.800 --> 38:14.598
♪♪

38:14.600 --> 38:17.099
[ BUZZER ]

38:17.101 --> 38:19.432
♪♪

38:19.434 --> 38:21.298
[ DOOR CLOSES ]

38:21.300 --> 38:29.898
♪♪

38:29.900 --> 38:31.132
HEY.

38:31.134 --> 38:34.598
NEVER THOUGHT
I'D SEE YOU AGAIN.

38:34.600 --> 38:36.432
WELL, YOU SHOULD HAVE
MORE FAITH.

38:36.434 --> 38:38.431
I TOLD YOU
THAT ISN'T MY THING.

38:38.433 --> 38:39.732
I KNOW.

38:43.367 --> 38:45.365
I'M HERE TO BAIL YOU OUT.

38:45.367 --> 38:52.065
♪♪

38:52.067 --> 38:58.765
♪♪

38:58.767 --> 39:00.798
HEY. Y'ALL READY?

39:00.800 --> 39:01.998
JUST ABOUT.

39:02.000 --> 39:04.098
I DON'T LIKE THIS ONE.

39:04.100 --> 39:05.965
YOU DIDN'T LIKE
THE LAST THREE EITHER, HONEY.

39:05.967 --> 39:07.665
COME ON, WE GOT TO GO.

39:07.667 --> 39:10.398
YOU KNOW HE DOESN'T WANT
TO WEAR THAT ANYTHING
ZORA DOESN'T HANDPICK?

39:10.400 --> 39:11.865
MM-HMM.

39:11.867 --> 39:13.198
MY LITTLE<i> GQ</i> MAN.

39:13.200 --> 39:15.465
HIS BIG SISTER
KEPT HIM FRESH, THOUGH.

39:15.467 --> 39:17.699
YES, SHE DID,
AND SHE WILL AGAIN.

39:17.701 --> 39:19.365
MWAH. [ CHUCKLES ]

39:19.367 --> 39:21.498
HEY, MAYBE WE CAN START
SOME KIND OF A GAME NIGHT

39:21.500 --> 39:24.031
OR SOMETHING.
SOMETHING FUN.

39:24.033 --> 39:25.965
UH, YEAH.
AS LONG AS IT'S NOT CHESS,

39:25.967 --> 39:28.498
'CAUSE YOU KNOW THAT LITTLE
BOY'S GOT AN UNFAIR ADVANTAGE.

39:28.500 --> 39:29.698
MM.

39:29.700 --> 39:31.432
THANKS FOR DOING THIS.

39:31.434 --> 39:33.065
NO NEED TO THANK ME.
IT'S ALL GOOD.

39:33.067 --> 39:34.798
WE JUST HAVE
SO LITTLE TIME LEFT WITH HER

39:34.800 --> 39:36.398
THAT I WANT HER TO GO OUT
INTO THE WORLD

39:36.400 --> 39:40.765
KNOWING THAT WE LOVE HER
AND THAT WE SUPPORT HER 100%.

39:42.867 --> 39:45.265
SHE'LL KNOW.

39:45.267 --> 39:48.265
I LOVE YOU SO MUCH.
[ CHUCKLES ]

39:48.267 --> 39:49.832
I LOVE YOU, TOO.

40:00.334 --> 40:01.565
MM.

40:01.567 --> 40:03.098
[ CHUCKLES ]

40:03.100 --> 40:05.632
ARE YOU HAVING
A HARD TIME DECIDING?

40:05.634 --> 40:08.465
UH, ON WHAT?

40:08.467 --> 40:10.598
WHAT YOU'RE GONNA WEAR.

40:10.600 --> 40:13.932
KIND OF.

40:13.934 --> 40:15.399
[ SIGHS ]

40:15.401 --> 40:16.599
WHAT DID I DO NOW?

40:16.601 --> 40:18.098
OH, NOTHING.

40:18.100 --> 40:20.865
NO, I WAS JUST THINKING
THAT IT MIGHT BE A GOOD IDEA

40:20.867 --> 40:22.265
FOR YOU TO TAKE OVER
THE LITTLE SAINTS

40:22.267 --> 40:23.432
WHILE SOPHIA'S HEALING.

40:23.434 --> 40:25.465
YEAH, IT'S A NO FOR ME,
THOUGH.

40:25.467 --> 40:27.132
COME AGAIN?

40:27.134 --> 40:29.498
I'M NOT GOOD WITH KIDS.

40:29.500 --> 40:33.232
ZORA, I THINK
IT'S COME TO A POINT NOW

40:33.234 --> 40:35.165
WHERE TAKING CARE
OF THE SOULS OF OTHERS

40:35.167 --> 40:38.665
WILL GIVE YOU A DEEPER SENSE
OF VALUE OF YOUR OWN.

40:38.667 --> 40:40.332
DO YOU NOT AGREE?

40:44.134 --> 40:47.265
WELL, I KNOW
HOW IT FEELS TO BE YOUNG.

40:47.267 --> 40:49.332
OH, YOU FEEL LIKE YOU HAVE
ALL THE TIME IN THE WORLD

40:49.334 --> 40:52.998
TO TRY THINGS OUT,
MAKE MISTAKES, BUT...

40:53.000 --> 40:58.332
ZORA, I CAN TELL YOU FROM
EXPERIENCE THAT THE MOMENT

40:58.334 --> 41:01.632
TO BE YOUR BEST SELF
IS RIGHT NOW.

41:05.500 --> 41:08.699
I DON'T WANT TO DO IT,
GRANDMA.

41:08.701 --> 41:11.365
AND EVEN IF I DID, I CAN'T.

41:14.434 --> 41:15.999
WHY NOT, ZORA?

41:16.001 --> 41:18.665
I'M 18 NOW.

41:18.667 --> 41:19.932
I'M LEAVING.

41:19.934 --> 41:24.732
♪♪

41:24.734 --> 41:27.398
AND WHEN, PRAY TELL,
IS THIS GRAND ESCAPE

41:27.400 --> 41:29.132
OF YOURS TAKING PLACE?

41:32.267 --> 41:33.932
IN ABOUT 10 MINUTES.

41:33.934 --> 41:37.465
♪♪

41:37.467 --> 41:38.398
ZORA?

41:38.400 --> 41:41.932
ZORA!

41:41.934 --> 41:51.531
♪♪

41:51.533 --> 42:00.932
♪♪

42:00.934 --> 42:10.532
♪♪

42:10.534 --> 42:19.999
